HB 288 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Boyer
Abstract: Permits the use of certain medical terminology in medical documentation.
Proposed law allows the term "miscarriage" be included after the term "spontaneous
abortion" in medical documentation, such as medical records or medical billing.
(Adds R.S. 22:46.1 and R.S. 40:1300.81)
